| Environment | Full Name                  | Purpose                                        | Who Uses It                  |
| ----------- | -------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------- |
| **DEV**     | Development                | Developers test and debug their code           | Developers                   |
| **SIT**     | System Integration Testing | Test how modules/services work together        | QA / Developers              |
| **NFT**     | Non-Functional Testing     | Performance, security, and scalability testing | QA / Performance Engineers   |
| **UAT**     | User Acceptance Testing    | Verify business requirements & workflows       | Business users / QA team     |
| **PROD**    | Production                 | Live environment for real users                | End users / DevOps / Support |


